           SHORT="A library thar provides emulation of smart cards"

cat <<EOF
CAC (Common Access Card) library
This library provides emulation of smart cards to a virtual card reader running
in a guest virtual machine. It implements DoD CAC standard with separate pki
containers (compatible coolkey), using certificates read from NSS.
EOF
